description:
Guess what’s finally here? Animation Deformers in Unreal are ready to shine in Sequencer! From setup to creating your very own custom Deformer, this video has it all. By the end, you’ll know ALL the secrets (and maybe even a few pro tricks 😏). Ready to level up your animations? Let’s gooooo! 🚀🔥

🧤Our courses : 
https://www.projprod.com/courses-1

🎁 Support my caffeine addiction fund and ensure I stay awake enough to keep creating content :
https://patreon.com/ProjProd?

♥️ Follow us on : 
Instagram : https://www.instagram.com/proj_production/
LinkedIn : https://www.linkedin.com/in/stephane-biava/

QOL (focus) console command:
AnimMode.PendingFocusMode 1

00:00 Intro
00:21 What is a Deformer?
00:49 Animator Kit Plugin
01:30 Grab Deformers via Sequencer
02:04 Camera Space Lattice Deformer
03:47 TRS Gizmo for Animation
04:39 QOL: Focus Pending Mode
05:25 Lattice Deformer
06:33 Anatomy of a Deformer
07:14 Create you own Deformer
08:58 Sculpt Deformer
09:50 Mask Bone Picker Control
11:30 Outro

#animation #deformer #unrealengine
